                    <statement>
                        <p>The function <m>h(y) = 24 + 18y</m> would find the height (in inches) of a paper birch tree which is <m>24</m> inches tall when it is planted, and grows by <m>18</m> inches per year. The independent variable <m>y</m> is the number of years after it is planted.<ol>
                            <li>
                                <p>What is the value of <m>h(3)</m>, including the correct units?</p>
                                <p><m>h(3) = </m><var name="$height" width="3" /> <var name="$units" form="popup" /></p>
