                <webwork>
                    <setup>
                        <var name="$f35">
                            <static>37</static>
                        </var>
                        
                        <pg-code>
                            $f35 = Real(37);
                        </pg-code>
                    </setup>
    
                    <statement>
                        <p>Drag the point on the <q>speed</q> axis to the desired input. Read the output values on the vertical axis to help you evaluate the function.</p>
